statements: SELECT * FROM quantum_calibration_parameters;
SELECT parameter_name, parameter_value FROM quantum_calibration_parameters WHERE device_id = 123;
SELECT parameter_name, parameter_value FROM quantum_calibration_parameters ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT AVG(parameter_value) AS avg_value FROM quantum_calibration_parameters;
SELECT MAX(parameter_value) AS max_value, MIN(parameter_value) AS min_value FROM quantum_calibration_parameters WHERE parameter_name = 'magnetic_field';
SELECT * FROM quantum_calibration_parameters WHERE device_id = 1 ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT device_id, parameter_name FROM quantum_calibration_parameters WHERE parameter_value > 0.5;
SELECT parameter_name, parameter_value FROM quantum_calibration_parameters WHERE device_id = 2 AND timestamp BETWEEN '2023-01-01' AND '2023-06-30';
SELECT DISTINCT device_id FROM quantum_calibration_parameters WHERE parameter_name LIKE '%bias%';
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_parameters FROM quantum_calibration_parameters WHERE timestamp > '2022-12-31';
SELECT * FROM quantum_devices;
SELECT device_name, calibration_date FROM quantum_devices WHERE device_id = 1;
SELECT device_id, device_name, calibration_date FROM quantum_devices ORDER BY device_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM quantum_devices WHERE calibration_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT device_name, JSONB_ARRAY_LENGTH(calibration_parameters) FROM quantum_devices;
SELECT * FROM quantum_devices WHERE device_id = 3;
SELECT device_name, calibration_date FROM quantum_devices ORDER BY calibration_date DESC;
SELECT device_id, calibration_parameters->'accuracy' AS accuracy FROM quantum_devices WHERE calibration_date > '2021-01-01';
SELECT device_name, log_date, calibration_success FROM calibration_logs INNER JOIN quantum_devices ON calibration_logs.device_id = quantum_devices.device_id WHERE calibration_success = TRUE;

SELECT DISTINCT device_name, count(log_id) AS total_logs FROM quantum_devices LEFT JOIN calibration_logs ON quantum_devices.device_id = calibration_logs.device_id GROUP BY device_name HAVING count(log_id) > 2;
SELECT * FROM quantum_devices;
SELECT device_name, calibration_date FROM quantum_devices;
SELECT device_name, calibration_type FROM quantum_devices ORDER BY calibration_date DESC;
SELECT device_name, calibration_value AS value FROM quantum_devices WHERE calibration_value > 0;
SELECT * FROM device_calibrations WHERE calibration_result < 0.5 ORDER BY calibration_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM quantum_devices ORDER BY device_id DESC;
SELECT device_name, calibration_date FROM quantum_devices WHERE calibration_value > 100;
SELECT device_name, calibration_type, calibration_date FROM quantum_devices WHERE calibration_date >= '2021-01-01' AND calibration_date <= '2021-12-31';

SELECT device_name, parameter_name, calibration_result FROM quantum_devices JOIN device_calibrations ON quantum_devices.device_id = device_calibrations.device_id JOIN calibration_parameters ON device_calibrations.parameter_id = calibration_parameters.parameter_id;
SELECT device_name, calibration_date, COALESCE(calibration_type, 'Not Defined') AS calibration_type FROM quantum_devices WHERE calibration_value IS NULL;
SELECT * FROM quantum_devices;
SELECT device_name, calibration_accuracy FROM quantum_devices WHERE calibration_accuracy > 8.0;
SELECT device_name, calibration_date FROM quantum_devices ORDER BY calibration_date DESC;
SELECT device_name, calibration_accuracy FROM quantum_devices WHERE calibration_accuracy < 6.0 ORDER BY device_name ASC;
SELECT device_name, calibration_date, calibration_accuracy FROM quantum_devices WHERE calibration_accuracy BETWEEN 7.0 AND 9.0;
SELECT * FROM quantum_devices;
SELECT device_name, calibration_date FROM quantum_devices WHERE calibration_accuracy > 0.95;
SELECT calibration_id, device_id, calibrated_by FROM calibration_history ORDER BY calibration_date DESC;
SELECT device_id, parameter_name, parameter_value FROM calibration_parameters WHERE parameter_value BETWEEN 0.5 AND 1.5 ORDER BY device_id ASC;
SELECT report_id, report_date, SUBSTRING(report_text, 1, 50) AS short_text FROM calibration_reports;
SELECT * FROM QuantumDevice;
SELECT device_name, calibration_date FROM QuantumDevice;
SELECT device_name FROM QuantumDevice WHERE calibration_status = 'calibrated';
SELECT device_name, calibration_user FROM CalibrationHistory JOIN QuantumDevice ON CalibrationHistory.device_id = QuantumDevice.device_id;
SELECT * FROM CalibrationParameters WHERE parameter_value > 10;
SELECT device_id, device_name FROM QuantumDevice ORDER BY device_name ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT * FROM CalibrationParameters WHERE parameter_value > 0.5 ORDER BY parameter_value DESC;
SELECT device_name, calibration_date, calibration_status FROM QuantumDevice JOIN CalibrationHistory ON QuantumDevice.device_id = CalibrationHistory.device_id WHERE calibration_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM HardwareComponents WHERE component_type = 'CPU' OR component_type = 'GPU';
SELECT * FROM CalibrationSettings WHERE setting_name = 'Temperature';
